*
!.gitignore
!generation/
!work/
!support_scripts_work/
!generation/.gitignore
!work/.gitignore
!support_scripts_work/.gitignore
# AI/vc is a local-only staging area for skill content (verbatim third-party docs + scratch).
# It stays on disk but is never tracked or published — the `*` rule above ignores it.
